w spawns . and have good pullers.<br><br>once you get to know the zone the trick is move slow and make sure pulled everything ,check in a 360 area<br><br><br>using this i did pog with 1 group with only 1 melee a warr and necro and shaman pet for melee dmg.<br><br><br><br>oooh ya dont forget a shaman they rule, and make everything work . <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/umirajtheenchanter.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Miraj the Enchanter</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(7/20/02 7:23:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2840.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: POG guide?</span><hr size=1> i heard something about the pogs being changed? anyone know anything bout this <p><img src=http://members.aol.com/mirajenchanter/smash.jpg><BR><BR>Board Ops<img src=http://www.members.aol.com/mirajenchanter/whack.gif>Your Sig</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/bayonaero.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=guy>Guy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Boardfellow</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(7/20/02 7:25:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2840.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: POG guide?</span><hr size=1> PoGs are still there, but they're bugged. They spawn on top of eachother (or something like that) so they're &quot;stuck&quot; in one spot and won't go chasing your raid for the time being. They're still there mind you, and if you move close to them they will aggro you and get themselves unstuck.<br><br>This might've been fixed in the last patch though. <p></p><i>